'''華城市'''（{{kor|諺=화성시|漢=華城市|羅=Hwaseong si|f=y}}），[[大韩民国|大韓民國]][[京畿道|京畿道]]下轄的一個市，位於該國首都[[首爾|首爾]]西南方48公里处。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://riverlab.berkeley.edu/wp/wp-content/uploads/LA205_SouthKorea_spring2019.pdf|title=Hwaseong Wetland|date=2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210620091105/http://riverlab.berkeley.edu/wp/wp-content/uploads/LA205_SouthKorea_spring2019.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.eaaflyway.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Wise-Use-of-the-Hwaseong-Wetlands_20210323_uploaded.pdf|title=Wise Use of the Hwaseong Wetlands Flyway Network Site|date=2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210620091057/https://www.eaaflyway.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Wise-Use-of-the-Hwaseong-Wetlands_20210323_uploaded.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://res.mdpi.com/d_attachment/sustainability/sustainability-11-00132/article_deploy/sustainability-11-00132.pdf|title=Value-Based Profiles of Visitors to a World Heritage Site: The Case of Suwon Hwaseong Fortress (in South Korea)|publisher=Sustainability|date=2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200215035707/https://res.mdpi.com/d_attachment/sustainability/sustainability-11-00132/article_deploy/sustainability-11-00132.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://res.mdpi.com/d_attachment/sustainability/sustainability-12-02182/article_deploy/sustainability-12-02182-v2.pdf|title=Temporal Distribution as a Solution for Over-Tourism in Night Tourism: The Case of Suwon Hwaseong in South Korea|publisher=Sustainability|date=2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125173216/https://res.mdpi.com/d_attachment/sustainability/sustainability-12-02182/article_deploy/sustainability-12-02182-v2.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref>城市名称来自于[[水原华城|水原华城]]，因华城市和水原市原同属水原郡；但水原华城在[[水原市|水原市]]，华城市实际上在水原华城西南方24公里处。

全市总面积688平方公里，人口864,687人（2021年4月）。<ref name="pop"/>

華城市境內工業發達，有食品加工、化工、機械、汽車等產業，[[三星電子|三星電子]]在此市設有先進製程的[[晶圓廠|晶圓廠]]。此外，農業、水產業及畜牧業亦在韓國各城市中較為發達。交通便利，共有三條高速公路經過。2000年與[[中國|中國]]的[[吴江市|吳江市]]成為姊妹城市。

